survey: two young people on the train in new jersey

currently use?
	fb
	ig
	tw
	snap
	gmail
	linkedin

privacy matters to you?
	depends

snapchat:
	i know it is not really private and they can see it
	i don't know why i keep using it

group organization:
	groupme
	polls

imagine a device with your own social network.
you get the device, one year of support.
how much do you think is a fair price for it?
	$200

comments on what they want:
	like a fliphone with internet
	you could have a package and charge more for extras
	market towards kids and older people, families
	older people who don't use iphones
